    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-6 flex gap-x-4">
    <a
      href="mailto:ericgarciafernandez18@gmail.com"
      target="_blank"
      class="hover:border-2 border-accent rounded-lg"><Email /></a
    >
    <a
      href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/eric-garc%C3%ADa-fern%C3%A1ndez/"
      target="_blank"
      class="hover:border-2 border-accent rounded-lg"><LinkedIn /></a
